<p id="notice"><%= notice %></p>
<div class="ui blue message">
  <div class="header">
    How scoring works
  </div>
  <p>The amount of marks per topic is added together, then multiplied multiplied by the time degredation function</p>
  <p>The time degredation function works by working out how many days it has been since the user has done that question. These are the current ratios:
  <ul>
  	<li><strong>0 to 10 days</strong>: multiply by 1 (full score)</li>
  	<li><strong>11 to 30 days</strong>: multiply by 0.8</li>
  	<li><strong>31 to 50 days</strong>: multiply by 0.5 (half score)</li>
  	<li><strong>51+ days</strong>: multiply by 0.2</li>

  </ul>
  (Remove this on release)
</div>
<% @subject.topics.each do |topic| %>
<div>
	<h3><%= topic.name %></h3>
	<strong>Score: </strong><%= '%.2f' % progress_in_topic(topic) %>
	<div class="ui cards">
	<% topic.questions.each do |question| %>
		<%= render "card", question: question %>
	<% end %>
	</div>
</div>

<% end %>
<%= link_to 'Edit', edit_subject_path(@subject) %> |
<strong><%= @subject.user.username %></strong>